Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target 1确认有高能量反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nova居然放激光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还是第一次...
